OL,3,CWorld champion mountain biker rides
OL,4,C7stanes in seven days
OL,6,FA former world champion took on a
OL,7,Fchallenge to promote the south of
OL,8,FScotland's mountain bike trails.
OL,10,FTracey Moseley was set the task of
OL,11,Ftrying all of the '7staines' trails
OL,12,Facross the area in the space of a week
OL,13,F- with her family in tow too.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
