FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775049066
OL,3,CWorld champion mountain biker rides
OL,4,C7stanes in seven days
OL,6,FFrom Monday a film documenting
OL,7,FMoseley's adventures is being released
OL,8,Fshowcasing not only the very best
OL,9,Fmountain biking trails in the South of
OL,10,FScotland but also exploring the
OL,11,Flandscapes, communities around them,
OL,12,Fand other tourist destinations nearby
OL,13,Flike stargazing, and beach walks.
OL,15,FThe project was supported by
OL,16,FDeveloping Mountain Biking in Scotland.
OL,18,FThe 7stanes include Dalbeattie, Forest
OL,19,Fof Ae, Glentress, Glentrool,
OL,20,FInnerleithen, Kirroughtree, Mabie, and
OL,21,FNewcastleton.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775049066
OL,3,CWorld champion mountain biker rides
OL,4,C7stanes in seven days
OL,6,FTracy said: "Back when the 7stanes
OL,7,Fwere launched in 2005, I made them a
OL,8,Fdestination to visit as I loved riding
OL,9,Fnew places.
OL,11,F"I loved them, and it felt like an
OL,12,Fadventure, each with its own special
OL,13,Ffeel and technical features to
OL,14,Fchallenge yourself with. Fast forward
OL,15,F20 years and as a mum I see the
OL,16,Fchallenges of modern life in trying to
OL,17,Fraise kids with the same spirit of
OL,18,Ffreedom and adventure.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775049066
OL,3,CWorld champion mountain biker rides
OL,4,C7stanes in seven days
OL,6,F"The 7stanes are a perfect
OL,7,Fintroduction to mountain biking for
OL,8,Ffamilies and new riders. They're also
OL,9,Fa hidden gem for families who want a
OL,10,Fsafe adventure out in nature. For just
OL,11,Fthe car park fee, you can have a full,
OL,12,Famazing day out with the family - with
OL,13,Fsomething for everyone. You don't need
OL,14,Fexpensive gear, just a bike, some
OL,15,Fplanning and enthusiasm.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775049066
OL,3,CWorld champion mountain biker rides
OL,4,C7stanes in seven days
OL,6,F"I wanted my son to feel the same
OL,7,Fenjoyment and voyage of discovery in
OL,8,Fhis journey as he discovers the
OL,9,F7stanes with his bike, as I did 20
OL,10,Fyears ago when I first visited them.
OL,11,FKids don't need loads of stuff, just
OL,12,Fgive them some outside space, the
OL,13,Ffreedom to move and play and a
OL,14,Fclassroom for learning in our
OL,15,Fincredible nature.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775049066
OL,3,CWorld champion mountain biker rides
OL,4,C7stanes in seven days
OL,6,F"This adventure was never about
OL,7,Fdistance or difficulty," said Tracy.
OL,8,F"It was about showing other families
OL,9,Fthat adventure can be simple ` it's
OL,10,Fabout time together, new experiences,
OL,11,Fand discovering what's in our forests
OL,12,Fand surrounding areas.
OL,14,F"You don't have to do all Stanes in 7
OL,15,Fdays, this project was always designed
OL,16,Fto be an inspiration piece. Encourage
OL,17,Fkids away from screens and into nature
OL,18,Fand you'll be rewarded by the amazing
OL,19,Fexperiences and lifetime memories you
OL,20,Fcan have together."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775049066
OL,3,CWorld champion mountain biker rides
OL,4,C7stanes in seven days
OL,6,FTracy, a former Downhill and Enduro
OL,7,FWorld Champion, has a deep connection
OL,8,Fwith the 7stanes ` the very trails
OL,9,Fthat helped shape her racing career
OL,10,Fand love for Scottish riding. Three
OL,11,Fdecades later, she's back to share
OL,12,Fthat same sense of discovery with her
OL,13,Fson, and to inspire families to make
OL,14,Ftheir own memories among the forests.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775049066
OL,3,CWorld champion mountain biker rides
OL,4,C7stanes in seven days
OL,6,FColena Cotter, Communications and
OL,7,FBusiness Support Manager at Developing
OL,8,FMountain Biking in Scotland, said:
OL,9,F"When Tracy approached us with this
OL,10,Fidea, we were excited to support and
OL,11,Fhelp make her vision come to life.
OL,12,FThis story perfectly captures what
OL,13,Fmountain biking in Scotland is all
OL,14,Fabout, nature, adventure, connection,
OL,15,Fand community.
OL,17,F"You don't have to be an experienced
OL,18,Frider to enjoy the 7stanes. These
OL,19,Fforests are places where families can
OL,20,Fplay, learn, and make memories
OL,21,Ftogether.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775049066
OL,3,CWorld champion mountain biker rides
OL,4,C7stanes in seven days
OL,6,F"We hope that this stunning film will
OL,7,Fhelp inspire other families out into
OL,8,Fthe forests, perhaps for the first
OL,9,Ftime, to have their own adventures."
OL,11,FDavid Hope-Jones, Chief Executive of
OL,12,Fthe South of Scotland Destination
OL,13,FAlliance, added: "This journey
OL,14,Fbeautifully showcases the South of
OL,15,FScotland as a world-class destination
OL,16,Ffor families and riders alike. The
OL,17,F7stanes are the heart of our cycling
OL,18,Fstory, offering everything from fun
OL,19,Fgreen trails to breathtaking views and
OL,20,Flocal experiences you'll never forget."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775049066
OL,3,CWorld champion mountain biker rides
OL,4,C7stanes in seven days
OL,6,F"What's truly special is how the
OL,7,FMoseley family's adventure highlights
OL,8,Fthe region's sense of welcome and
OL,9,Fpossibility. Whether you're new to
OL,10,Fbiking, travelling with children, or
OL,11,Fjust looking for time together in
OL,12,Fnature, the South of Scotland has
OL,13,Fsomething for everyone.
OL,15,F"Our forests, communities, and
OL,16,Flandscapes are made for adventure `
OL,17,Fand we hope Tracy's story inspires
OL,18,Fmore families to come, explore, and
OL,19,Fcreate their own unforgettable
OL,20,Fmemories here."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
